java.lang.Object
org.infinispan.metadata.impl.PrivateMetadata

      public static PrivateMetadata empty()
      Returns:
      An empty instance of PrivateMetadata, i.e., without any metadata stored.

    • getBuilder

      public static PrivateMetadata.Builder getBuilder(PrivateMetadata metadata)
      Returns a PrivateMetadata.Builder with the metadata stored by metadata.

      If metadata is null, an empty PrivateMetadata.Builder instance is created.

      Parameters:
      metadata - The PrivateMetadata to copy from.
      Returns:
      The PrivateMetadata.Builder instance.
